Package controller

Class CreateNewUserScreenController

java.lang.Object
controller.CreateNewUserScreenController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class CreateNewUserScreenController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This is the controller class for the createNewUserScreen.fxml document. It creates new users for the application, either salespersons or administrators, the latter of which are permitted to create new users themselves.

    • onSubmit

      public void onSubmit(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent) throws SQLException, IOException
      This method is an event handler on the Submit button. It validates the data and then inserts it into the database.
      Parameters:

    • onTypeSelect

      public void onTypeSelect(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
